              <div class="ph-chip"><div class="pc-lbl">Satisfaction Rate</div><div class="pc-val">98.7%</div><div class="pc-sub">From 2,400+ repairs</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fc fc-l"><div class="fc-lbl">Avg. Repair Time</div><div class="fc-val">2 hrs <span class="fc-badge">Fast</span></div></div>
          <div class="fc fc-r"><div class="fc-lbl">Happy Customers</div><div class="fc-val">2,400+</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="si"><div class="si-num">2,400+</div><div class="si-lbl">Devices Repaired</div></div>
      <div class="si"><div class="si-num">98%</div><div class="si-lbl">Satisfaction Rate</div></div>
      <div class="si"><div class="si-num">2 hrs</div><div class="si-lbl">Avg. Turnaround</div></div>
      <div class="si"><div class="si-num">90 days</div><div class="si-lbl">Repair Warranty</div></div>
    </div>

    <section class="svc-sec">
      <img class="svc-bg" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555774698-0b77e0d5fac6?w=1200&q=60&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">
      <div class="svc-inner">
        <div class="svc-head">
          <div>
            <div class="pill"><span class="pill-dot"></span>What We Do</div>
            <h2 class="stitle">Expert repair for <em>every issue</em></h2>
            <p class="sdesc">Professional services backed by warranty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-grid">
          <div class="sc" onclick="go('services')"><div class="sc-icon-wrap"><i data-feather="smartphone"></i></div><div class="sc-arr">↗</div><h3>Screen Repair</h3><p>Fast replacement for all major brands. Original panels, touch calibrated, warranty included.</p></div>
          <div class="sc" onclick="go('services')"><div class="sc-icon-wrap"><i data-feather="battery"></i></div><div class="sc-arr">↗</div><h3>Battery Replacement</h3><p>Restore original battery life with genuine OEM cells. Done in under 45 minutes.</p></div>
          <div class="sc" onclick="go('services')"><div class="sc-icon-wrap"><i data-feather="droplet"></i></div><div class="sc-arr">↗</div><h3>Water Damage</h3><p>Ultrasonic cleaning to save your device before corrosion sets in. Act fast.</p></div>
          <div class="sc" onclick="go('services')"><div class="sc-icon-wrap"><i data-feather="settings"></i></div><div class="sc-arr">↗</div><h3>Software Issues</h3><p>Fix crashes, freezes, and boot loops. OS updates and full factory restoration available.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="steps-sec">
      <div class="steps-inner">
        <div class="steps-head">
          <div class="pill"><span class="pill-dot"></span>How It Works</div>
          <h2 class="stitle" style="font-size:42px;">Simple. <em>Stress-free.</em></h2>
          <p class="sdesc" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto;">Four easy steps from broken to brand-new.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-row">
          <div class="step-it"><div class="step-num">1</div><h4>Bring or Ship</h4><p>Walk in or mail us your device. Free diagnostic — no obligation to repair.</p></div>
          <div class="step-it"><div class="step-num">2</div><h4>Get a Quote</h4><p>Transparent pricing with zero hidden fees. Approve before we begin.</p></div>
          <div class="step-it"><div class="step-num">3</div><h4>Expert Repair</h4><p>Certified techs fix your device with premium parts and pro-grade tools.</p></div>
          <div class="step-it"><div class="step-num">4</div><h4>Quality Check</h4><p>Full function test and 90-day warranty before it leaves our bench.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testi-sec">
      <div class="testi-inner">
        <div class="testi-head">
          <div class="pill" style="margin:0 auto 18px;"><span class="pill-dot"></span>Customer Reviews</div>
          <h2 class="stitle">What customers <em>say</em></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testi-grid">
          <div class="tc"><div class="tc-q">"</div><p class="tc-txt">My iPhone screen was completely shattered. Fixed in 2 hours and looks brand new! Great pricing, no surprises.</p><div class="tc-bot"><div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;"><div class="tc-av">JM</div><div class="tc-name"><strong>James Martinez</strong><span>Verified Customer</span></div></div><div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div></div></div>
          <div class="tc"><div class="tc-q">"</div><p class="tc-txt">Dropped my Samsung in water and thought it was gone. These guys saved it! Professional, fast, and fair pricing.</p><div class="tc-bot"><div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;"><div class="tc-av">ER</div><div class="tc-name"><strong>Emily Rodriguez</strong><span>Verified Customer</span></div></div><div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div></div></div>
          <div class="tc"><div class="tc-q">"</div><p class="tc-txt">Battery dying by noon every day. Replaced it quickly and now I get through the full day. Highly recommend to everyone!</p><div class="tc-bot"><div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;"><div class="tc-av">DK</div><div class="tc-name"><strong>David Kim</strong><span>Verified Customer</span></div></div><div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-sec">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <img class="cta-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512941937669-90a1b58e7e9c?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="smartphone">
        <div class="cta-ov"></div>
        <div class="cta-txt"><h2>Ready to get your phone fixed?</h2><p>Walk in, book online, or call us. We make it simple.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

