          <p>Our certified technicians stay current with the latest techniques and use only genuine or high-quality replacement components. We know how vital your phone is — we treat every device as if it were our own.</p>
          <div class="perks">
            <div class="pk"><div class="pk-ic"><i data-feather="shield"></i></div><div class="pk-body"><strong>90-Day Repair Warranty</strong><span>Every repair is fully covered. Peace of mind guaranteed.</span></div></div>
            <div class="pk"><div class="pk-ic"><i data-feather="search"></i></div><div class="pk-body"><strong>Free Diagnostics</strong><span>Know exactly what's wrong before committing to anything.</span></div></div>
            <div class="pk"><div class="pk-ic"><i data-feather="zap"></i></div><div class="pk-body"><strong>Same-Day Service</strong><span>Most repairs completed within 2 hours, walk-out ready.</span></div></div>
            <div class="pk"><div class="pk-ic"><i data-feather="award"></i></div><div class="pk-body"><strong>Premium Parts Only</strong><span>Genuine or OEM-grade components for lasting results.</span></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
