              <p class="mv-desc">We exist to provide every person in Cebu with an honest, affordable, and professional smartphone repair experience — delivered with transparency, speed, and genuine care. No runarounds. No hidden costs. Just reliable service you can trust.</p>
              <div class="mv-pillars">
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot"></span>Honest, transparent service with no hidden fees</div>
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot"></span>Certified, precision-driven repairs for all brands</div>
