              <p class="mv-desc">We envision a future where no one has to worry about where to bring their broken device. Onin's will be the first name that comes to mind — synonymous with quality craftsmanship, integrity, and lasting relationships with every customer we serve.</p>
              <div class="mv-pillars">
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot mvp-dot-v"></span>Become Cebu's undisputed #1 repair destination</div>
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot mvp-dot-v"></span>Expand accessible, quality repair across the region</div>
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot mvp-dot-v"></span>Build long-term trust through every interaction</div>
                <div class="mv-pillar"><span class="mvp-dot mvp-dot-v"></span>Set the standard for excellence in the industry</div>
              </div>
            </div>
